para.preformatted:
Facing issues when running the LD_PRELOAD related command, edit the Makefile. In the run command, replace the following line:
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/dpf/bin/linx64:
    export LD_PRELOAD=/dpf/bin/linx64/libiomp5.so:/dpf/bin/linx64/libmkl_core.so:/dpf/bin/linx64/libmkl_intel_thread.so:/tp/stdc++/libstdc++.so.6:
These lines must be replaced with the following content:
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/aisol/dll/linx64:
    export LD_PRELOAD=/tp/IntelCompiler/2023.1.0/linx64/lib/intel64/libiomp5.so:/tp/IntelMKL/2024.2.0/linx64/lib/intel64/libmkl_core.so:/tp/IntelMKL/2024.2.0/linx64/lib/intel64/libmkl_intel_thread.so:/tp/stdc++/libstdc++.so.6:
